taskbody.example:
The following screen capture and sample code show a search query and the JCL that is
generated. For more information about the ISPF Search-For utility and examples of ISPF Search-For
query strings, see the ISPF User's Guide, Volume II.
Sample Remote z/OS File Search query

//USERID1 JOB ,
// MSGCLASS=H,MSGLEVEL=(1,1),TIME=(,4),REGION=144M,COND=(16,LT)
//SUPERC   EXEC PGM=ISRSUPC, 
//             PARM=('SRCHCMP,NOSEQ,ALLMEMS,ANYC') 
//OUTDD   DD SYSOUT=* 
//NEWDD    DD DISP=SHR,DSN=USERID.TEST
//SYSIN    DD * 
SRCHFOR 'A' 
SRCHFORC 'B',+ 
SRCHFORC 'C''D',+2
SRCHFOR 'EF G',W  
SELECT MEMBER1,MEMBER2,MEMBER3 
/* 
//
